<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to SpeakAnyWay Pro üéâ</title>
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light only">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f6f8fb;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 640px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 120px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 16px auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #111827;
      font-size: 26px;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 26px 0 10px;
    }
    p { line-height: 1.6; margin: 12px 0; }
    ul, ol { padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0; }
    li { margin: 6px 0; }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      background-color: #2abed1;
      color: #000000 !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .muted {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .note {
      background: #f7f9fc;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .highlight {
      background: #ecfeff;
      border: 1px solid #67e8f9;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 18px 0;
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: #eef0f4;
      margin: 26px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 26px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .footer a { color: #7645ef; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%# --- Dynamic limits (safe defaults) --- %>
  <% pro_price = (@pro_price || "$20/month") %>
  <% pro_comm_limit = (@pro_comm_limit || @user&.comm_account_limit || 3) %>
  <% demo_comm_limit = (@demo_comm_limit || 10) %>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <a href="https://speakanyway.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <%= image_tag @logo.url, alt: "SpeakAnyWay Logo" %>
      </a>
    </div>

    <h1>Welcome to SpeakAnyWay Pro üéâ</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Built for families, classrooms, and professionals supporting multiple communicators.
    </p>

    <p>Hi <%= @user.name.blank? ? "there" : @user.name %>,</p>

    <p>
      Thanks for choosing <strong>SpeakAnyWay Pro</strong>!  
      You now have powerful tools to support communication across home, school, therapy, and community settings.
    </p>

    <!-- ‚≠ê DEMO COMMUNICATOR HIGHLIGHT -->
    <div class="highlight">
      <h2 style="margin-top:0;">‚≠ê New in Pro: Demo Communicator Accounts</h2>
      <p>
        Your Pro plan includes <strong><%= demo_comm_limit %> Demo Communicator Accounts</strong> to start.
        These are designed specifically for <strong>modeling, organizing, and planning</strong>
        ‚Äî without requiring a username or passcode.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Model AAC</strong> during therapy or instruction without signing in</li>
        <li><strong>Organize boards</strong> by student, classroom, activity, or routine</li>
        <li>Create <strong>lesson-specific or temporary boards</strong> (field trips, themes, events)</li>
        <li>Safely demonstrate AAC to families or teams without touching a child's account</li>
        <li>Plan and build boards ahead of time, then copy them where needed</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="muted">
        Demo Communicators are perfect for SLPs, teachers, aides, and caregivers who need flexibility without friction.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>‚ú® What's included in Pro</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong><%= pro_comm_limit %> Paid Communicator Accounts</strong>  
        (username + passcode for switching devices and remote access)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong><%= demo_comm_limit %> Demo Communicator Accounts</strong>  
        (no login ‚Äî ideal for modeling and organization)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>MySpeak+</strong> for every Paid Communicator  
        (public access, emergency & medical info, instant QR access)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Unlimited Supporters</strong>  
        (read-only access for teachers, aides, caregivers, and family)
      </li>
      <li>
        Full access to <strong>AI features</strong> (word suggestions, layouts, board generation)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Advanced analytics</strong> to understand usage and progress
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Priority support</strong> when you need help fast
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>PDF + QR exports</strong> for portable AAC anywhere
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>üöÄ Get set up in minutes</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Create your paid Communicator Accounts for individuals.</li>
      <li>Use Demo Communicators to model AAC or organize boards by theme.</li>
      <li>Build boards using AI for routines, classroom, or community use.</li>
      <li>Export boards as <strong>PDF + QR</strong> for offline or shared access.</li>
      <li>Invite Supporters so everyone stays aligned.</li>
    </ol>

    <p style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="<%= @login_link || @frontend_url %>" class="btn">
        Open Your Pro Dashboard
      </a>
    </p>

    <p class="muted" style="text-align:center;">
      If the button doesn't work, copy this link:<br>
      <span style="word-break:break-all;">
        <%= @login_link || @frontend_url %>
      </span>
    </p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>üí° Pro tips</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Use Demo Communicators to test layouts before assigning them.</li>
      <li>Name demos by activity (e.g., ‚ÄúSnack Time‚Äù, ‚ÄúMorning Routine‚Äù).</li>
      <li>Review analytics to refine real-world vocabulary use.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="footer">
      Need help, onboarding support, or want to add more Communicators?<br>
      Visit <a href="https://app.speakanyway.com/pricing" target="_blank">pricing</a> or reply to this email.
      You can also reach us at
      <a href="mailto:help@speakanyway.com">help@speakanyway.com</a>.
      <br><br>
      Current Pro pricing: <strong><%= pro_price %></strong>. Cancel anytime.
      <br><br>
      ‚Äî The SpeakAnyWay Team üíú
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
